data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!!! This beautiful 5BR, 4.5BTH is located in a sought after quiet neighborhood on a cul-de-sac. LOTS of natural light! Open foyer leads to formal living area & dining room. Kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, gas cooktop, granite countertops, lots of cabinet space and a peaceful breakfast nook overlooking a private backyard!! Oversized den with a fireplace and built in shelving! Finished basement w/ fireplace for possible in-law suite, office or playroom. Full sized attic with permanent stairs & plenty of storage space! Sellers are motivated & offering a 10k paint & flooring allowance along with a one year home warranty! Schedule your showing today! Agents, please see agent only remarks.
